        </h2>
        <div
          class="c4"
        >
          <ul
            class="c15"
          >
            <li>
              To open the developer console by right clicking on the popup & selecting "Inspect"
            </li>
            <li>
              You can find the code on the "Sources" panel, in
               
              <code>
                sandbox.html
              </code>
               &gt; 
              <code>
                (no domain)
              </code>
               after executing it.
            </li>
            <li>
              You also can use 
              <code>
                debugger;
              </code>
               in the code.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
